Package: singboxvpn
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: sing-box (>= 1.9), libc6, libgtk-3-0
Maintainer: Hau Tran <tranthienhau@gmail.com>
Description: Flutter desktop client for Sing-box VPN
